						               													<description>Outwit your friends with pharmacy finesse, daring diet and exercise, noble nutrition and lifestyle choices while avoiding terrible temptations given to you by your friends.  Strategize how to get the best blood sugar score and earn the admiration of your family, friends, and general practitioner.  Pit yourself against other diabetic warriors in the ultimate battle of diabetes management, Battlebetes.&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Battlebetes is a card drafting and scoring game played in three rounds where each round each player is trying to be the closest to 100.  Each round has two parts: &amp;ldquo;Drafting Cards&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Throwing and Scoring&amp;rdquo;.  The player with the highest score after three rounds wins. The first part is a &amp;quot;draft and pass&amp;quot; dynamic like &amp;quot;sushi go&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;7 wonders&amp;quot;.  This leaves players with five important choices that will ultimately decide their chances of winning.  Do you: stack one card or balance cards, directly attack others or choose a card just to prevent another from getting it, save it for later or spend now? In the scoring phase each player throws their resulting food tokens like dice (each side has a number) adding any modifiers obtained resulting in their round score.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
